1.0.name: wordpress/calicotek-floating-social-slider
1.0.description: this simple plugin adds a social slider to the sides top or bottom of any website so far it supports facebook, twitter, google plus, and site email... when the user of the site hovers over the social sliders they slide out using java script,.. social profiles can be configured via a admin settings page... Everything is working now for most part can position left and right and add options that function :)
